== 反響 ==
《夜行動物》在威尼斯影展首映時獲得了正面好評，多半稱讚亞當斯、葛倫霍、夏儂、強森和琳妮的表現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/nocturnal-animals-film-review-venice-release-tom-ford-amy-adams-jake-gyllenhaal-a7221856.html|title=Nocturnal Animals Review: Tom Ford returns with a superb, painstakingly crafted movie sure to pick up awards|work=[[Independent.co.uk|Independent.co.uk]]|accessdate=2016-09-03|archive-date=2016-11-15|archive-url=https://archive.today/20161115021023/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/nocturnal-animals-film-review-venice-release-tom-ford-amy-adams-jake-gyllenhaal-a7221856.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於226條評論，持有73％的新鮮度，平均評分為6.9 / 10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nocturnal_animals |title=Nocturnal Animals |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011054919/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nocturnal_animals |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分67（滿分100），好評居多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/nocturnal-animals|title=Nocturnal Animals|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-09-22|archive-date=2016-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213020740/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/nocturnal-animals|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

